name: Special Edition Card for jesus - The Paladin
description:
No one can hurt him because Paladin's skin is like steel!

He was a partner needed by Necromancer and Alchemist. As a knight as well as a defender who is equipped with powerful armor, Paladin has the main job of protecting his two friends with his strength during this journey. So, Necromancer can more easily attack the enemy and Alchemist can heal if someone gets injured or opens the other potions from the bag he carries.
